<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.278091>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Clymenura snaiko sp. nov. uncini. A, chaetiger 1 row in situ; B, chaetiger 14 row in situ; C, chaetiger 14 uncinal head; D, chaetiger 15 row in situ. A – B at actual relative sizes, scale bars 50 µm, C – D scale bars 20 µm." ;
